    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo specifies cdma2000 wireless data AAA (Authentication, Authorization, Accounting) requirements associated with third generation wireless architecture that supports roaming among service providers for traditional PPP and Mobile IP services.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
